{
  "stem": "10162.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at the end of this period, whatever it was, they took us over to Fabrik Allendorf, which was about, I don't know, maybe an hour walk through this pine forest to a very, very large underground factory complex, which I know now was owned by Dynamit Nobel.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was one of the largest ammunition factories of Nazi Germany, grenade and-- and bomb factories.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we did the whole thing from, from, from A to Z, you know, filling with this poisonous-- he would call it tri-- tri something, I forget-- the grenades.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- I did work for a short time at the filling station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then soon after that, they put me at the very end of the mass production, you know, when the things just come rolling down, where my job was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was-- I think I was probably the tallest there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, I, I had broad shoulders and round face, something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They thought I was just strong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had to pick these grenades, the way they rolled up, and flip it-- put it over into a, a little trolley kind of thing that had grates.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And probably 16 would go into one of these things and that rolled right out of the building and where, on the other side, were the Russian prisoners of war who would-- who would put it in trains.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I worked there until April '45, until April 6 or something like that, '45.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I don't know, nine months, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was better conditions in the-- definitely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the beginning, we especially appreciated the better conditions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then, of course, it got-- you know, it got very difficult.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
